caption.p: Histopathological evaluation of the kidney of the control and stressed groups, samples were stained with hematoxylin and eosin, the arrows represent pathological changes in tissue: ( a) control groups: normal tissue ×200; ( b) H 2O 2 group: congestion ×200; ( c) H 2O 2 + Argan group: congestion ×200; ( d) H 2O 2 + Argan + Syzygium aromaticum essential oil group: normal tissue ×100.
